Package model

Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
model.User
model.Administrator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Administrator extends User
Represents an Administrator in the Hospital Management System (HMS). This class extends the User class and provides additional functionality specific to administrators, such as managing staff and handling refill requests.
Since:
2024-11-18
Version:
1.0
Author:
Lee Kuan Rong Shane, Lim Wee Keat, Tan Wen Rong, Yeoh Kai Wen
